MANTIS: A report for Adira

Mohammad Nozari

18 April, 2016

Summary

This report is written to help Adira’s staff verify the collected data which will be used by MANTIS project. In this section, a summary of the log file is introduced.

The number of records after cleaning the data and remove the duplicates is 1661 and the dataset has 45 columns.
